    <item>
      <title>乔治·桑托斯将在联邦法院认罪，避免审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/george-santos-set-to-plead-guilty-in-federal-court-avoid-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，美国前众议员乔治桑托斯预计将于周一承认联邦欺诈指控。在被曝出捏造大部分人生经历后，他的国会职业生涯就此中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/george-santos-set-to-plead-guilty-in-federal-court-avoid-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 18:37:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将在 11 月 5 日前投入 3.7 亿美元用于数字和电视业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/harris-to-spend-370-million-on-digital-and-tv-in-push-to-nov-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈里斯-沃尔兹竞选团队表示，计划在劳动节至 11 月 5 日期间投入至少 3.7 亿美元用于数字和电视广告，这是竞选的最后阶段，主要争取战场州的选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/harris-to-spend-370-million-on-digital-and-tv-in-push-to-nov-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 18:03:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克誓言关闭特斯拉巴西业务，但将维持服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/musk-vows-to-close-x-s-brazil-operations-will-maintain-service</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据社交媒体平台周六发布的帖子，埃隆·马斯克的特斯拉汽车 X 将关闭其在巴西的业务，但仍在该国提供服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/musk-vows-to-close-x-s-brazil-operations-will-maintain-service</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:46:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨称，Mpox 紧急状态有机会纠正错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/mpox-who-emergency-status-chance-to-redress-mistakes-in-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨表示，将非洲迅速蔓延的羊痘疫情宣布为全球卫生紧急事件，使世界卫生组织有机会纠正此前对非洲大陆帮助不大的错误。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/mpox-who-emergency-status-chance-to-redress-mistakes-in-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 16:21:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰总统图斯克就北溪管道破坏事件发表看法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/poland-s-tusk-weighs-into-controversy-over-nord-stream-sabotage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克 (Donald Tusk) 似乎介入了 2022 年北溪天然气管道破坏事件的争议，呼吁停止对谁应对袭击负责的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/poland-s-tusk-weighs-into-controversy-over-nord-stream-sabotage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩与以色列冲突加剧 面临停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/lebanon-suffers-from-total-blackout-as-clashes-with-israel-intensify</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于真主党和以色列之间的跨境袭击愈演愈烈，国营电力公司表示其天然气已经耗尽，黎巴嫩全国陷入“全面停电”困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/lebanon-suffers-from-total-blackout-as-clashes-with-israel-intensify</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“高昂”住房成本给民主党带来压力 促使哈里斯提出 25,000 美元税收抵免法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/kamala-harris-housing-plan-targets-gen-z-millennial-voters-hurt-by-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯承诺采取行动降低住房成本，这一举措降低了年轻人、少数族裔和低收入选民等民主党核心选民对总统竞选的热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-17/kamala-harris-housing-plan-targets-gen-z-millennial-voters-hurt-by-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
